Author: George Anton <george@antonpictures.com>
Date:   Wed Apr 15 00:40:13 2026 -0700

    fix: register module in sys.modules before exec_module (Python 3.13)
    
    Python 3.13 dataclass decoration fails during dynamic import when the
    module is not yet in sys.modules — produces:
      'NoneType' object has no attribute '__dict__'
    
